        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34284580/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34284580/" class="">第112页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3874308/" class=" " title="合欢">合欢</a>
                (everything comes full circle)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="34284580">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">一个人彻悟的程度，恰恰等于他所受苦的深度。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-02-10 22:38</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                一个人彻悟的程度，恰恰等于他所受苦的深度。
